<subSubSection id="C37065004C64FFF86D1EFC7BFC82C0F8" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BD5368B4C64FFF86D1EFC7BFC82C0F8" blockId="3.[264,1325,759,1876]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<emphasis id="B91EEA994C64FFF86D1EFC7BFE17C091" box="[312,435,919,944]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Etymology</emphasis>
. — The species is dedicated to Maximilian Schwarz in whose collection the 
